name: Just Be Tee
description:
We plucked Milo out of the sky and put him on a shirt just for you.  Give a sense of calm and fluffiness to everyone you meet!  

Available in Small, Medium, and Large

name: Milo Pocket Art
description:
A Milo for your pocket!  This hand cast, hand painted resin sculpture is just the right size for keeping with you in a pants pocket, or for putting on your desk/nightstand/shoulder to remind you that inner peace is a deep breath away.  Milo is always calm and content, and his happy little mug reminds you that despite everything, you can be that way too.  The box that Milo comes in also makes for a great display for your Milo Pocket Art.  Milo stands at 1.5 inches tall and 3 inches wide.  Buy one and enjoy him, or buy two and give one to a friend!
Signed and dated by the artist.

name: Highly Overrated Tee
description:
Milo knows the value of daydreaming, and of letting yourself be carried away on the breeze of imagination.  Let your mom/teacher/slave-driving boss know that you can't be contained.  This cotton tee will tell everyone where your priorities are, and that your genius knows no bounds.

Available in Medium, Large, and XL
